Subject: Putting the Problem Back in Problem Solving
Description: So many people want to solve problems, they often skip over the important step of trying to really understand a problem and making sure they are solving the right problem. This discussion will focus on some exercises that can help you examine problems in the tech space (and life in general), to better hone your problem solving skills.  Speakers include:Lana Krolikowski - Track: Tech  - Duration: 1 hour
